sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant CMS as Headless CMS

    Note over U,CMS: View Educational Insights

    U->>F: Open Educational Insights
    U->>F: Select category/article (optional search/filter)
    F->>B: GET /content?query=...&category=...
    B->>CMS: Fetch articles/resources
    alt CMS unavailable / error
        CMS-->>B: Error / timeout
        B-->>F: 503/500 Content unavailable
        F-->>U: Show "Content unavailable" message
    else Success
        CMS-->>B: Articles/resources
        B-->>F: 200 OK + content list/content item
        F-->>U: Display content
    end